				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[2. Interest Recovery]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="30" y="360" width="497" height="130" uuid="38cfc9bb-2eba-4ddd-a0cd-d4ffc9f5426f"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" markup="html"/>
				<text><![CDATA[Interest on the Loan shall begin to accrue from the date of debit to the Company’s Bank Account simultaneously with the Company’s disbursement of the Loan by issuing Pay Order / Demand Draft or otherwise, without the Company concerning itself with the receipt of such disbursement by the beneficiary / recipient and with the realisation of such Pay Order / Demand Draft or the time taken in such realisation.<br><br>
The interest will be computed based on the principal outstanding balance on a daily basis. This interest amount will be debited to the facility account itself thereby recovering the interest component of the EMI. Excess funds over and above the EMI deposited by the Borrower/s into the account will be adjusted against the principal outstanding, unless instructed by the Borrower to consider it as an advance EMI. On the other hand, if sufficient funds are not deposited into the account then the interest debited will show as an unauthorized overdraft and the account will be categorized as a delinquent account.]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<staticText>
